WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:03.266
Guo Yiming, can you stop sleeping?

2
00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:06.900
Miss Lin, I have something to tell you.

3
00:00:06.933 --> 00:00:08.266
Let's go out and talk

4
00:00:12.133 --> 00:00:13.066
Miss Lin

5
00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:15.166
I know because of the Lins

6
00:00:15.166 --> 00:00:16.666
Guo Yuning saved me this time

7
00:00:16.666 --> 00:00:17.833
I don't want to be with you.

8
00:00:18.966 --> 00:00:22.366
I know I shouldn't say this in my capacity

9
00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:25.033
But Mr. Gu is really not what you think

10
00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:27.066
I have followed Mr. Gu for so many years

11
00:00:27.066 --> 00:00:29.466
His heart is actually very soft and kind

12
00:00:29.466 --> 00:00:30.666
He has already liked you

13
00:00:30.666 --> 00:00:31.766
It's just that he doesn't dare to admit it.

14
00:00:31.766 --> 00:00:33.600
I like what you do

15
00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:35.733
Do you think he did that to me?

16
00:00:35.733 --> 00:00:37.100
Because I like it

17
00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:39.900
Mr. Gu, he just doesn't know how to love someone

18
00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:41.266
Because after he turned 10

19
00:00:41.266 --> 00:00:43.033
No one loves him anymore

20
00:00:43.166 --> 00:00:45.366
When you suddenly disappeared from the hospital

21
00:00:45.366 --> 00:00:47.000
Mr. Gu is having a meeting abroad

22
00:00:47.066 --> 00:00:49.266
I will come back to you as soon as I hear the news.

23
00:00:49.266 --> 00:00:50.900
When you were taken away by Mr. Wei

24
00:00:50.900 --> 00:00:52.566
He pretended not to care on the surface

25
00:00:52.566 --> 00:00:54.800
In fact, secretly, I have been sending people to investigate everywhere

26
00:00:55.166 --> 00:00:56.800
I thought you were taken advantage of by Mr. Wei

27
00:00:56.900 --> 00:00:59.166
He would rather offend Mr. Wei than bring you back

28
00:00:59.166 --> 00:01:00.400
Not even installed

29
00:01:00.666 --> 00:01:02.666
In the month since you left Mr. Gu

30
00:01:02.700 --> 00:01:04.866
He asked the coffee shop owner to take care of you more

31
00:01:04.866 --> 00:01:07.366
No matter how busy I am, I will make time to see you

32
00:01:07.366 --> 00:01:09.800
He can't rest assured until you get home safely

33
00:01:10.933 --> 00:01:12.233
Then why is he

34
00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:15.033
Never told me this

